  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_PPT_ch7_page_057_6",
    "text": "Clearly, this vector equation (1) holds if we choose all c's zero, because then it becomes 0 = 0.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.05833334574927912,
      0.565806877227645,
